# Title: Potential Windows Defender Tampering Via Wmic.EXE
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-12-11
# Level: high
# Description: Detects potential tampering with Windows Defender settings such as adding exclusion using wmic
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1047, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_namespace_defender.yml

CommandLine="*/Namespace:\\\\root\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Defender*" OriginalFileName="wmic.exe" OR Image="*\\WMIC.exe"